  "sample_input": "# VesselFlow State Definition Prompt\n\nUsando os dados do VesselFlow, defina o estado operacional atual do sistema, dos contratos existentes e do processo de nomeacao.\n\nIdentifique:\n\n1. dominios operacionais;\n2. entidades;\n3. evidencias disponiveis;\n4. lacunas;\n5. contratos e restricoes;\n6. gates de qualificacao, sincronizacao e nomeacao;\n7. riscos e fragilidade;\n8. deltas necessarios;\n9. fluxo computavel de nomeacao;\n10. Cube/Cupula state;\n11. relatorio final.\n\nO retorno deve incluir State Snapshot, Operational Graph, Domain Map, Contract Map, Nomination Flow, Gate Matrix, Evidence Manifest, Risk/Fragility Index, Delta Recommendations, Cube State, Replay e Report.",
  "expected_outputs": [
    "State Snapshot",
    "Operational Graph",
    "Domain Map",
    "Evidence Manifest",
    "Gate Matrix",
    "Risk/Fragility Summary",
    "Delta Recommendations",
    "Cube/Cupula State",
    "Cockpit Replay",
    "Micrograph Timeline",
    "Internal Review Report"
  ],
  "blocked_actions": [
    "client_facing_claim",
    "nomination_execution",
    "implementation_execution",
    "production_activation"
  ],
  "instruction": "Define the operational state for this vertical. Produce state, evidence, gates, deltas, Cube/Cupula state, replay, timeline and internal report. Do not authorize external use or implementation."
